---
// src/components/WhyChooseUs.astro
// This component highlights the key reasons to choose HomeTech Repair.
---
<section id="why-us" class="section why-us-section">
    <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Why Choose HomeTech Washer Repair</h2>
        <div class="why-us-grid">
            <div class="feature-item card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M8 4a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v4.086l2.043 2.043a.5.5 0 0 1-.707.707l-2.2-2.2A.5.5 0 0 1 7.5 9V4.5A.5.5 0 0 1 8 4z"/><path d="M8 16A8 8 0 1 0 0 8a8 8 0 0 0 8 8zm0-1A7 7 0 0 1 1 8a7 7 0 1 1 14 0A7 7 0 0 1 8 15z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Same‑Day Service</h3>
                <p>Rapid response across Mumbai, Thane & Navi Mumbai to get your washer back on track quickly.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M5.338 1.59 8 0l2.662 1.59A7 7 0 0 1 15 7.07c0 4.363-2.94 7.16-6.563 8.74a1.7 1.7 0 0 1-1.374 0C3.44 14.23.5 11.433.5 7.07A7 7 0 0 1 5.338 1.59z"/><path d="M10.97 6.97a.75.75 0 0 1 1.07 1.05l-3.992 4.99a.75.75 0 0 1-1.08.02L3.324 9.384a.75.75 0 1 1 1.06-1.06l2.094 2.093 4.492-5.446z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Genuine Parts & 90‑Day Warranty</h3>
                <p>We use quality parts and back our labour with a written warranty for peace of mind.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-item card">
                <div class="feature-icon">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M13 7c0 1.105-.672 2-1.5 2S10 8.105 10 7s.672-2 1.5-2S13 5.895 13 7zM5.5 9C6.328 9 7 8.105 7 7S6.328 5 5.5 5 4 5.895 4 7s.672 2 1.5 2z"/><path d="M1 14s-1 0-1-1 1-4 5.5-4S11 12 11 13s-1 1-1 1H1zm9 0s-1 0-1-1 1-3 3.5-3S16 13 16 14s-1 1-1 1h-5z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <h3>Washer Brand Experts</h3>
                <p>Experienced with LG, Samsung, Whirlpool, IFB, Bosch, Godrej, Haier & more.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .why-us-section {
        background:
            radial-gradient(600px 240px at -10% 0%, rgba(0,123,255,0.08), transparent 60%),
            radial-gradient(600px 240px at 110% 0%, rgba(255,193,7,0.1), transparent 60%),
            linear-gradient(180deg, var(--secondary-color), #fff);
    }
    .why-us-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: clamp(1rem, 1.2vw, 2rem);
        text-align: left;
    }
    .card {
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
        border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: clamp(1.25rem, 1rem + 0.8vw, 1.75rem);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease, background 0.3s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    }
    .card:hover { transform: translateY(-6px); box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.12); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); }

    .feature-item { display: grid; align-content: start; gap: 0.5rem; }
    .feature-icon {
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        width: 48px;
        height: 48px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(0,123,255,0.1);
        color: var(--primary-color);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .feature-item h3 { font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1rem + 0.4vw, 1.25rem); }
    .feature-item p { color: #5c6770; line-height: 1.7; }
</style>
